    {
      "name": "2. Update My Profile",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
          { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"display_name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"bio\": \"Music lover and producer 🎵🎧\",\n  \"location\": \"Cairo\",\n  \"favorite_genres\": [\"Electronic\", \"House\"],\n  \"social_links\": {\n    \"instagram\": \"johndoe_ig\",\n    \"x\": \"johndoe_x\"\n  },\n  \"is_private\": false\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/me",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["users", "me"]
        },
        "description": "## 2. Update My Profile\n\nUpdates one or more fields on the authenticated user's profile. Only valid fields included in the request body will be modified. Any fields not listed below are silently ignored.\n\n**Authentication:** Required\n\n### Request Body (All Optional)\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| `display_name` | String | Max 50 chars. |\n| `bio` | String | Max 500 chars. |\n| `location` | String | Max 100 chars. |\n| `favorite_genres` | Array | Array of string genres. |\n| `social_links` | Object | Keys: `instagram`, `x`, `facebook`, `website`. |\n| `is_private` | Boolean | Toggles profile visibility. |"
      },
      "response": [
        {
